{"lemma":"خَمْسَةُ","slug":"خَمْسَةُ","root":"خمس","root_slug":"خمس","root_link":"/words/roots/خمس","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خَمْسَةُ","root":"خمس","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","num"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11497","n11503"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%92%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"num","gloss":"masculine of خَمْسَة (ḵamsa, “five”)","tags":["form-of","masculine"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the five digits of the hand"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one fifth"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *ḫamišum.\n\nFrom the root خ م س (ḵ m s); compare خَمْسَة (ḵamsa, “five”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11497","headword_ar":"خمّسهُ","root":"xms","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxomiysN","text_ar":"تَخْمِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it five."},{"kind":"text","text":"(EshSheybánee and K, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waH~adahu","text_ar":"وَحَّدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it to be five-cornered; five-angled; pentagonal."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xam~asato","text_ar":"خَمَّسَتْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She brought forth her fifth offspring."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bkr","text_ar":"بكر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xm~shu","text_ar":"خمّسهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it five-fifths."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xm~s liA@moraA^atihi","text_ar":"خمّس لِا@مْرَاَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EinodahaA","text_ar":"عِنْدَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He remained five nights with his wife"},{"kind":"text","text":": and in like manner the verb is used in relation to any saying or action. (TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sab~aEa","text_ar":"سَبَّعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxomiysN","text_ar":"تَخْمِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"watering"},{"kind":"text","text":"of land or seedproduce"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the fifth day, counting the day of the next preceding watering as the first;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"watering"},{"kind":"text","text":"of land"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarobiyE","text_ar":"تَرْبِيع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n11503","headword_ar":"خَمْسَةٌ","root":"xms","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) masc.; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamosN","text_ar":"خَمْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", fem.; (S;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Five;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain number."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamosapu rijaAlK","text_ar":"خَمْسَةُ رِجَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Five men"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamosu nisowapK","text_ar":"خَمْسُ نِسْوَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Five women"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EinodiY xamosapu daraAhimo","text_ar":"عِنْدِى خَمْسَةُ دَرَاهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have five dirhems"},{"kind":"text","text":"], with refa: and if you please, you incorporate the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"d","text_ar":"د"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamosap d~araAhima","text_ar":"خَمْسَة دَّرَاهِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: but when you prefix"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":"to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drAhm","text_ar":"دراهم"},{"kind":"text","text":", you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EinodiY xamosapu Ald~araAhimi","text_ar":"عِنْدِى خَمْسَةُ الدَّرَاهِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have the five dirhems"},{"kind":"text","text":"], with damm; and may not incorporate, because you have incorporated the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"l","text_ar":"ل"},{"kind":"text","text":"into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"d","text_ar":"د"},{"kind":"text","text":": and in the case of a fem. n. you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EinodiY xamosu","text_ar":"عِنْدِى خَمْسُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alquduwri","text_ar":"القُدُورِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have the five cooking-pots"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxamosapu Ald~araAhimi","text_ar":"الخَمْسَةُ الدَّرَاهِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"These five dirhems"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and, if you please,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~araAhimu","text_ar":"الدَّرَاهِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", using it in the manner of an epithet: and in like manner [you use the other nouns of number] to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$arapN","text_ar":"عَشَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[inclusive]. (S.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SumonaA xamosFA mina Al$~ahori","text_ar":"صُمْنَا خَمْسًا مِنَ الشَّهْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We fasted"},{"kind":"text","text":"during a period of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"five"},{"kind":"text","text":"nights"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the month"},{"kind":"text","text":"with their"},{"kind":"page_break","n":811},{"kind":"text","text":"days]; making"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layaAlK","text_ar":"لَيَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to predominate over"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ay~aAm","text_ar":"اَيَّام"},{"kind":"text","text":", when you do not mention the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ay~Am","text_ar":"ايّام"},{"kind":"text","text":", though the fasting is in the day; because the night of each day precedes the day: but when you mention the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ay~Am","text_ar":"ايّام"},{"kind":"text","text":", you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SumonaA xamosapa A^ay~aAmK","text_ar":"صُمْنَا خَمْسَةَ اَيَّامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We fasted five days"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (ISk, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEaD~u biAlxamosi","text_ar":"يَعَضُّ بِالخَمْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bites the fingers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"these being [five in number and] of the fem gender: (Ham p. 790:) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamosN","text_ar":"خَمْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"five fingers."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 76.) [Respecting a peculiar pronunciation of the people of El-Hijáz, and a case in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamosap","text_ar":"خَمْسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is imperfectly decl., see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamosapa Ea$ara","text_ar":"خَمْسَةَ عَشَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", masc.; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamosa Ea$orapa","text_ar":"خَمْسَ عَشْرَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", fem.;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fifteen."},{"kind":"text","text":"For variations thereof, see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E$r","text_ar":"عشر"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}